2025-09-10 15:30:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:27 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:30:27 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy, what can you tell me about giant crabs?
2025-09-10 15:30:27 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:28 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:28 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:28 [INFO] Can continue: Giant Crabs? Why, I used to haul up a few of those<br>whenever I set my nets around Rimmington.
2025-09-10 15:30:28 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:29 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:29 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:29 [INFO] Can continue: Why the interest?
2025-09-10 15:30:29 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:30 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:30 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:30:30 [INFO] Can continue: I need to get some Giant Crab Meat and Kelp. Can<br>you tell me where I can get some?
2025-09-10 15:30:30 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:31 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:31 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:31 [INFO] Can continue: Well, the only thing I can think to do is to go down<br>there and look to see if there are any left.
2025-09-10 15:30:31 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:33 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:30:33 [INFO] Can continue: Go down there? What do you mean?
2025-09-10 15:30:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:34 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:34 [INFO] Can continue: As in under the water!
2025-09-10 15:30:34 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:35 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:35 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:35 [INFO] Can continue: Tell me, can you get your hands on a fishbowl?
2025-09-10 15:30:35 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:36 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:30:36 [INFO] Can continue: I'm sure I will be able to if I put my mind to it, why<br>do you ask?
2025-09-10 15:30:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:38 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:38 [INFO] Can continue: Well, I know how to rig up a handy set of breathing<br>gear that can allow you to keep air inside the fishbowl.
2025-09-10 15:30:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Can continue: You just put the barrel of air on your back, with the<br>fishbowl over your head, and then dive over the side.
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Can continue: It should hold enough air to keep you alive for quite<br>some time.
2025-09-10 15:30:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:40 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:30:40 [INFO] Can continue: That sounds pretty dangerous...
2025-09-10 15:30:40 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:41 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:41 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:41 [INFO] Can continue: Not at all. I'll even weigh anchor with the chain<br>somewhere easy to reach so you can climb out easily<br>enough if you run into trouble.
2025-09-10 15:30:41 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Can continue: I'm still not happy about this...
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Can continue: Well, I can't think of any other way to check. If you<br>come up with a better plan then feel free to tell me.
2025-09-10 15:30:42 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:43 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:43 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
2025-09-10 15:30:43 [INFO] Can continue: In the meantime I'll wait, and if you want me to take<br>you diving I'll be ready.
2025-09-10 15:30:43 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:30:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:30:45 [INFO] Can continue: Murphy
