2025-09-10 15:35:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:35:24 [INFO] Can continue: Nung
2025-09-10 15:35:24 [INFO] Can continue: You's gotta get me somefing to make dese hides to a<br>cloak and flippers and hat, den I lets you have all the<br>big crunchy claws you can get.
