2025-09-10 15:35:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:35:25 [INFO] Can continue: Nung
2025-09-10 15:35:25 [INFO] Can continue: But it not be easy
2025-09-10 15:35:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:35:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:35:26 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:35:26 [INFO] Can continue: Well I'll do it. What do I need? An item of ancient<br>power? Something from the deepest, darkest dungeon in<br>the world?
