2025-09-10 16:50:35 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:50:35 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:50:35 [INFO] Can continue: Indeed. You all know the target. Get changed quick<br>and be ready to take your positions.
