2025-09-10 16:51:03 [INFO] java.awt.Rectangle[x=2,y=275,width=17,height=50]
2025-09-10 16:51:05 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:05 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:05 [INFO] Can continue: Move along, citizen.
2025-09-10 16:51:05 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:07 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:07 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:51:07 [INFO] Can continue: Wait! I have some information that you need to hear.
2025-09-10 16:51:07 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:08 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:08 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:08 [INFO] Can continue: What is it?
2025-09-10 16:51:08 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:10 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:51:10 [INFO] Can continue: There are some bandits disguising themselves as guards!<br>I think they're planning to attack the delegation from<br>Varlamore!
2025-09-10 16:51:10 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:11 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:11 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:11 [INFO] Can continue: Surely you can't be serious?
2025-09-10 16:51:11 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Can continue: It's true! One of them infiltrated your guards and stole<br>some uniforms. He came right through here earlier with<br>them.
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Can continue: The one with the large bag? I thought I didn't<br>recognise him, but then it's so hard to keep up. We get<br>through guards so quickly around here for some<br>reason...
2025-09-10 16:51:12 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:13 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:13 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:51:13 [INFO] Can continue: So what do we do? Should we warn the delegation?
2025-09-10 16:51:13 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:14 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:14 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:14 [INFO] Can continue: And risk a panic? No. Better we deal with this now<br>while they're safe in the palace. Do you know how<br>many bandits there are?
2025-09-10 16:51:14 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:14 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:15 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:51:15 [INFO] Can continue: Four in total.
2025-09-10 16:51:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:16 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:16 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:16 [INFO] Can continue: Right, we can work with that. You get out there and<br>point them out. With them being disguised, you'll need<br>to keep a close eye out for any guard who looks or<br>acts differently to the others.
2025-09-10 16:51:16 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:17 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:17 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:17 [INFO] Can continue: Don't go too far. If the bandits intend to attack the<br>delegation, they'll either be here in the square or on the<br>eastern road between the square and the bank.
2025-09-10 16:51:17 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:18 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:51:18 [INFO] Can continue: Return to me once you've found all four and we'll take<br>them all at the same time.
2025-09-10 16:51:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:51:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:51:19 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:51:19 [INFO] Can continue: Alright, I'll get to it.
2025-09-10 16:51:19 [INFO] Continue
