2025-09-10 16:52:01 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:01 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:52:01 [INFO] Can continue: Alright, I've pointed out all the bandits.
2025-09-10 16:52:01 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:03 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:03 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:03 [INFO] Can continue: Good work. I'll signal my guards to bring them in...
2025-09-10 16:52:03 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:04 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:06 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn signals to his guards and the bandits are quickly<br>arrested.
2025-09-10 16:52:06 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:07 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:07 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:07 [INFO] Can continue: That could have ended up quite nasty if not for you.<br>Once again, good work.
2025-09-10 16:52:07 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Can continue: So what happens now?
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Can continue: The bandits will be interrogated. If all goes well, we'll<br>get some useful information out of them.
2025-09-10 16:52:08 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:09 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:09 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:09 [INFO] Can continue: Speaking of which... given it was you who found them in<br>the first place, you might be able to offer some support.<br>Would you be willing to help?
2025-09-10 16:52:09 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:10 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:52:10 [INFO] Can continue: Of course! Where do you need me?
2025-09-10 16:52:10 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:11 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:11 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:11 [INFO] Can continue: Come with me. We'll use the cell on the palace roof for<br>the interrogations. It's nice and out of the way.
2025-09-10 16:52:11 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:13 [INFO] LOADING
2025-09-10 16:52:14 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn escorts you to the palace roof.
2025-09-10 16:52:14 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:15 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:15 [INFO] Can continue: Ah, nilsal, sergeant.
2025-09-10 16:52:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla! I... I'm sorry, but I wasn't expecting you<br>here.
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Can continue: Well, all that politics downstairs was getting a bit dry,<br>but then I heard there'd been a bit of a commotion. I<br>thought I'd come see what the fuss was all about. You<br>don't mind, do you?
2025-09-10 16:52:16 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Can continue: Well, no, it's just...
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Can continue: Wonderful! And you! Who are you?
2025-09-10 16:52:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:19 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:52:19 [INFO] Can continue: Hello there. I'm PLAYER_NAME.
2025-09-10 16:52:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:20 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:20 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME? Kuani! Pleased to meet you. Crown Prince<br>Itzla Arkan, heir to the Sun Throne, at your service.
2025-09-10 16:52:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:21 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:21 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:21 [INFO] Can continue: Tell me, PLAYER_NAME, are you the one who caught these<br>would-be assassins?
2025-09-10 16:52:21 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:22 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:22 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:52:22 [INFO] Can continue: That's right.
2025-09-10 16:52:22 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:24 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:24 [INFO] Can continue: Well, then why don't you and I ask this one a few little<br>questions. You don't mind, do you, sergeant?
2025-09-10 16:52:24 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Can continue: Not at all, but...
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Can continue: Excellent! Let's get started then.
2025-09-10 16:52:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:28 [INFO] [GAME] You have unlocked a new music track: <col=e00a19>The Burning Sun
2025-09-10 16:52:28 [INFO] LAG DETECTED 1365ms
2025-09-10 16:52:33 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:33 [INFO] Can continue: Nilsal to you, iknami. I hear you managed to get<br>yourself into a spot of bother.
2025-09-10 16:52:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Can continue: I'm not telling you anything.
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Can continue: Ah, tetamo! Such a shame. No matter though! We'll<br>have you talking in no time.
2025-09-10 16:52:34 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:35 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:35 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:35 [INFO] Can continue: Now, you'll need to forgive me, but I'm a bit new<br>around here, so your customs are not familiar to me.<br>Tell me, iknami, what's the preferred method of<br>interrogation in these parts?
2025-09-10 16:52:35 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Can continue: You're asking me how you should interrogate me?
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Can continue: Well, it just seemed polite to ask. We have all sorts of<br>fun methods back home in Varlamore. We could give<br>one or two of them a go if you want?
2025-09-10 16:52:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Can continue: If I want?
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Can continue: Absolutely! Now, what are your thoughts on chicken?
2025-09-10 16:52:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:38 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:38 [INFO] Can continue: Chicken?
2025-09-10 16:52:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Can continue: Oh, PLAYER_NAME, do you not have chickens here? Sorry,<br>again, all this is quite new to me.
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Can continue: Yes, we have chickens. The farms around here have<br>loads.
2025-09-10 16:52:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:40 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:40 [INFO] Can continue: Well, then why the confusion? Have you never seen<br>one before? Oh you poor sheltered thing. Did your<br>parents never show you the wonders of the<br>countryside?
2025-09-10 16:52:40 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:41 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:41 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:41 [INFO] Can continue: I know what a chicken is!
2025-09-10 16:52:41 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:42 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:42 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:42 [INFO] Can continue: Well, why didn't you say so?
2025-09-10 16:52:42 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Can continue: I don't know what game you're playing, but it won't<br>work on me!
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Can continue: No game at all, iknami. The reason I ask is because<br>one of our preferred methods in Varlamore involves<br>just a small amount of fire, and you'd never believe it,<br>but the smell of human flesh once it gets going...
2025-09-10 16:52:43 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:44 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:44 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:44 [INFO] Can continue: You're going to cook me?
2025-09-10 16:52:44 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Can continue: Cook? No, not at all! That would imply I'm going to eat<br>you, and I'm not a barbarian! Though, it would be<br>interesting to know if it tastes like chicken as well...
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Can continue: Alright, enough! I'll tell you what you want!
2025-09-10 16:52:45 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:46 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:46 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:46 [INFO] Can continue: Kuani!
2025-09-10 16:52:46 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:47 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:47 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:47 [INFO] Can continue: So who are you working for?
2025-09-10 16:52:47 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Can continue: I don't know their name. They just paid us to attack<br>the delegation. They didn't look to be from around<br>here. I reckon it was one of your lot!
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Can continue: Why did they want you to attack the delegation?
2025-09-10 16:52:48 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:50 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:50 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:50 [INFO] Can continue: They didn't say, but that priest... he was the target!
2025-09-10 16:52:50 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:51 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:51 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:51 [INFO] Can continue: So a Varlamorian paid you to assassinate the Teokan?<br>You're not giving me much to go on.
2025-09-10 16:52:51 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:53 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:53 [INFO] Can continue: Bandit
2025-09-10 16:52:53 [INFO] Can continue: That's all I know!
2025-09-10 16:52:53 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:54 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:54 [INFO] Can continue: Hmm...
2025-09-10 16:52:54 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:55 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:55 [INFO] Can continue: Well, I think we're done here. Come, PLAYER_NAME.
2025-09-10 16:52:55 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:52:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:52:57 [INFO] LAG DETECTED 1121ms
2025-09-10 16:52:59 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:52:59 [INFO] Can continue: I think we got what we needed there.
2025-09-10 16:52:59 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:00 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:00 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:53:00 [INFO] Can continue: You're sure he told you everything?
2025-09-10 16:53:00 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:01 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:01 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:01 [INFO] Can continue: Oh yes. The fear of being cooked will do that to a<br>person. All total rubbish of course! Imagine burning<br>someone alive! We're much more civilised over in<br>Varlamore.
2025-09-10 16:53:01 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:02 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:02 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:02 [INFO] Can continue: We just cut out their heart while it's still beating<br>instead.
2025-09-10 16:53:02 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:03 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:03 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:53:03 [INFO] Can continue: I can't tell if you're joking or not...
2025-09-10 16:53:03 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:04 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:04 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:04 [INFO] Can continue: Anyway, sounds like there'll be some work to do when<br>we get back home. An assassination attempt on the<br>Teokan of Ralos... Concerning stuff. First up though,<br>I'd better get back to the politics!
2025-09-10 16:53:04 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:06 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:06 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:06 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME, once we've got these papers signed, you lot<br>will be free to travel to Varlamore for the first time! No<br>more needing explicit permission. You can come and go<br>as you please!
2025-09-10 16:53:06 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:08 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:08 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:08 [INFO] Can continue: Now, it's entirely up to you of course, but given we<br>have you to thank for stopping this plot, I'd be very<br>keen if you'd join me in Varlamore to continue the<br>investigation.
2025-09-10 16:53:08 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:09 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:09 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:09 [INFO] Can continue: No need to decide now, but if you do wish to accept<br>my offer, just speak to Regulus Cento outside the<br>eastern gates of this city.
2025-09-10 16:53:09 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:10 [INFO] Can continue: Prince Itzla Arkan
2025-09-10 16:53:10 [INFO] Can continue: Now, they'll be missing me downstairs. Timoiva, and<br>may the sun light your way!
2025-09-10 16:53:10 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:14 [INFO] Can continue: Itzla departs.
2025-09-10 16:53:14 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:15 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:53:15 [INFO] Can continue: Well, that was interesting...
2025-09-10 16:53:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:17 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:17 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:53:17 [INFO] Can continue: Not every day the heir to a far-off land comes and<br>interrogates one of your prisoners?
2025-09-10 16:53:17 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:53:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:53:18 [INFO] Can continue: Sergeant Tobyn
2025-09-10 16:53:18 [INFO] Can continue: Oddly enough, no. This will be an interesting report to<br>write. And on that note, I'd best get to it. All the best,<br>adventurer. Thank you for your help.
2025-09-10 16:53:18 [INFO] Continue
